summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting an Easement for storm drain and sanitary sewer purposes and a Deed for street purposes over Tracts 50, 52, 53, 55 and 56 of the State of Washington Commissioner of Public Lands Subdivision of the N.E. 1/4, E. 1/2 of N.W. 1/4 and N.E. 1/4 of S.W. 1/4, Section 10, Tp. 25 N. , R. 4 E., W.M. and laying off Mithun Place Northeast (Coast Guard Site; RW 8204).
